title: NHK Great Nature 2013 Madagascars Forests of Stone Needles 720p
description:
Madagascar's Forests of Stone Needles

Nature Documentary hosted by Naoya Murayama, published by NHK broadcasted as part of NHK Great Nature series in 2013 - English narration. 
http://docuwiki.net/images/f/f0/Madagascar-s-Forests-of-Stone-Needles-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------
The superb scenery of Tsingy - a treasure trove of wildlife is revealed, including lemurs, a forest of limestone needles on which you can't walk with bare feet, and trees growing on dry ground.
